      "bodyHtml": "<div class='max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8'><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-primary'><div class='card-body'><h1 class='card-title text-2xl font-bold leading-snug'>Should leading brand manufacturers supply private label brands to retailers_ Calibrating the trade-offs</h1><div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2'><span class='badge badge-primary badge-outline'>Industrial Marketing Management</span><span class='badge badge-secondary badge-outline'>Vol. 76 (2019), pp. 192-202</span><span class='badge badge-accent badge-outline'>model</span></div><p class='mt-2 text-base-content/70'>저자: Sandra J. Milberg</p><p class='text-xs text-base-content/50'>DOI: 10.1016/j.indmarman.2018.09.001</p></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 1 — 초록 번역</h2><div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'><div><p class='text-sm font-semibold text-base-content/60 mb-2'>영문 원문</p><blockquote class='border-l-4 border-base-300 pl-4 italic text-sm text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed'>The consolidation of retailers across markets has considerably altered the competitive dynamics between leading brand manufacturers and retailers. The era in which brand manufacturers dictate the game to compliant retailers is long gone. Nowadays, with more equal negotiation power retailers are no longer just channel partners but rather business partners with whom to build business-to-business relationships. This has become apparent especially since retailers have developed their own private label brands (PLB) and actively seek brand manu- facturers to supply them. For brand manufacturers supplying PLB may bring potential bene fits but may also harm pro fits. Thus, this research investigates conditions under which a leading brand manufacturer would be better or worse o ff in terms of pro fitability producing PLB for retailers. Using a game theoretic model, we calibrate the trade-o ffs between the shelf space devoted by the retailer to the manufacturer brand and the amount of profit required from supplying the PLB necessary to counteract cannibalization and to generate pro fits for the manufacturer, under di fferent levels of uncertainty regarding the availability of alternative suppliers. Calibrating these trade-o ffs provides brand manufacturers clear guidelines for negotiations with retailers re- garding shelf space allocation and wholesale prices to be pro fitable supplying PLB.</blockquote></div><div><p class='text-sm font-semibold text-base-content/60 mb-2'>한국어 번역</p><blockquote class='border-l-4 border-primary/40 pl-4 text-sm text-base-content leading-relaxed'>리테일러의 PLB를 공급할지는 shelf space와 이윤 trade-off, 그리고 대체 공급자 불확실성에 따라 달라진다.</blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 2 — 핵심 주장 (1분 설명용)</h2><div class='alert alert-success mb-6'><span class='font-bold'>한 줄 요약:</span><span class='ml-2'>리테일러의 PLB를 공급할지는 shelf space와 이윤 trade-off, 그리고 대체 공급자 불확실성에 따라 달라진다.</span></div><ul class='steps steps-vertical'><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>연구 질문</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>The consolidation of retailers across markets has considerably altered the competitive dynamics between leading brand manufacturers and retailers.</p></div></li><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>핵심 발견</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>Calibrating these trade-o ffs provides brand manufacturers clear guidelines for negotiations with retailers re- garding shelf space allocation and wholesale prices to be pro fitable supplying PLB.</p></div></li><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>이론적·실무적 기여</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>리테일러의 PLB를 공급할지는 shelf space와 이윤 trade-off, 그리고 대체 공급자 불확실성에 따라 달라진다.</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 3 — 근거 표</h2><div class='overflow-x-auto'><table class='table table-zebra table-sm w-full'><thead><tr><th>#</th><th>핵심 주장</th><th>근거</th><th>위치</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class='text-xs italic'>The consolidation of retailers across markets has considerably altered the competitive dynamics between leading brand manufacturers and retailers.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class='text-xs italic'>The era in which brand manufacturers dictate the game to compliant retailers is long gone.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class='text-xs italic'>Nowadays, with more equal negotiation power retailers are no longer just channel partners but rather business partners with whom to build business-to-business relationships.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 4 — 연구 방법 분해</h2><ul class='timeline timeline-vertical'><li><div class='timeline-start timeline-box bg-primary text-primary-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 1</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>PLB 공급의 수익성 trade-off를 게임이론으로 캘리브레이션했다.</p></div><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary'></div></div><hr class='bg-primary'/></li><li><hr class='bg-secondary'/><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-secondary'></div></div><div class='timeline-end timeline-box bg-secondary text-secondary-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 2</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>핵심 변수·사례·대상을 정리한다.</p></div><hr class='bg-secondary'/></li><li><hr class='bg-accent'/><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-accent'></div></div><div class='timeline-start timeline-box bg-accent text-accent-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 3</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>저자들이 사용한 분석틀/모형을 적용한다.</p></div><hr class='bg-accent'/></li></ul><p class='mt-4 text-sm'><b>재현 가능성 평가:</b> 부분 재현 가능</p></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 5 — Limitation 분리</h2><div class='alert alert-error mb-4'><span class='font-bold'>A. 논문이 스스로 인정한 한계</span><span class='ml-2'>가정이 단순해서 현실 복잡성을 다 담지 못한다</span></div><div class='collapse collapse-arrow bg-warning/10'><input type='checkbox'/><div class='collapse-title font-medium'>B. 논문이 언급하지 않았지만 비판적으로 의심할 점</div><div class='collapse-content'><p>실증 데이터로의 외적 검증이 추가로 필요하다.</p></div></div></div></div></div>",
