      "excerptKo": "홈마켓 압력이 완만하면 가까운 시장, 과도하면 먼 시장으로 수출을 재배분하는 U자/역U자 관계를 보인다. STEP 2 — 핵심 주장 (1분 설명용) 한 줄 요약: 홈마켓 압력이 완만하면 가까운 시장, 과도하면 먼 시장으로 수출을 재배분하는 U자/역U자 관계를 보인다. 연구 질문 This study uses an organizational change perspective to analyze…",
      "bodyHtml": "<div class='max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8'><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-lg border-l-4 border-primary'><div class='card-body'><h1 class='card-title text-2xl font-bold leading-snug'>The trade-off between institutionally proximal and distal markets_ The impact of home market pressures on firms’ export market selection</h1><div class='flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2'><span class='badge badge-primary badge-outline'>Industrial Marketing Management</span><span class='badge badge-secondary badge-outline'>Vol. 76 (2019), pp. 98-108</span><span class='badge badge-accent badge-outline'>quantitative</span></div><p class='mt-2 text-base-content/70'>저자: Hsiang-Lin Cheng</p><p class='text-xs text-base-content/50'>DOI: 10.1016/j.indmarman.2018.08.005</p></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 1 — 초록 번역</h2><div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'><div><p class='text-sm font-semibold text-base-content/60 mb-2'>영문 원문</p><blockquote class='border-l-4 border-base-300 pl-4 italic text-sm text-base-content/80 leading-relaxed'>This study uses an organizational change perspective to analyze firms&#x27; export market selection (EMS) to adapt to home country market pressures. We argue that firms&#x27; strategic objectives infl uence whether they will enter institutionally proximal or distal markets. A model with two curvilinear (U-shaped and inverted U-shaped) relationships is found by testing 1940 Taiwanese export firms based on two o ﬃcial datasets. The model shows that firms are more likely to increase their exports to institutionally proximal markets and to decrease their exports to institutionally distal markets if they have an increasing but still controllable degree of competitive and marketing pressures in the home country. This response represents an incremental change by exporting firms. However, firms increase their exports to institutionally distal markets while decreasing their exports to in- stitutionally proximal markets if they have an excessively increasing degree of competitive and marketing pressures in the home country. This response represents a radical change by exporting firms. We find that export firms&#x27; strategic objectives in choosing di fferent organizational change styles (incremental or radical) are highly related to this trade-o ff in their EMS decision making.</blockquote></div><div><p class='text-sm font-semibold text-base-content/60 mb-2'>한국어 번역</p><blockquote class='border-l-4 border-primary/40 pl-4 text-sm text-base-content leading-relaxed'>홈마켓 압력이 완만하면 가까운 시장, 과도하면 먼 시장으로 수출을 재배분하는 U자/역U자 관계를 보인다.</blockquote></div></div></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 2 — 핵심 주장 (1분 설명용)</h2><div class='alert alert-success mb-6'><span class='font-bold'>한 줄 요약:</span><span class='ml-2'>홈마켓 압력이 완만하면 가까운 시장, 과도하면 먼 시장으로 수출을 재배분하는 U자/역U자 관계를 보인다.</span></div><ul class='steps steps-vertical'><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>연구 질문</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>This study uses an organizational change perspective to analyze firms&#x27; export market selection (EMS) to adapt to home country market pressures.</p></div></li><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>핵심 발견</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>We find that export firms&#x27; strategic objectives in choosing di fferent organizational change styles (incremental or radical) are highly related to this trade-o ff in their EMS decision making.</p></div></li><li class='step step-primary'><div class='text-left ml-4'><p class='font-semibold'>이론적·실무적 기여</p><p class='text-sm text-base-content/70'>홈마켓 압력이 완만하면 가까운 시장, 과도하면 먼 시장으로 수출을 재배분하는 U자/역U자 관계를 보인다.</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 3 — 근거 표</h2><div class='overflow-x-auto'><table class='table table-zebra table-sm w-full'><thead><tr><th>#</th><th>핵심 주장</th><th>근거</th><th>위치</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td class='text-xs italic'>This study uses an organizational change perspective to analyze firms&#x27; export market selection (EMS) to adapt to home country market pressures.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td class='text-xs italic'>We argue that firms&#x27; strategic objectives infl uence whether they will enter institutionally proximal or distal markets.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td class='text-xs italic'>A model with two curvilinear (U-shaped and inverted U-shaped) relationships is found by testing 1940 Taiwanese export firms based on two o ﬃcial datasets.</td><td>Abstract</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 4 — 연구 방법 분해</h2><ul class='timeline timeline-vertical'><li><div class='timeline-start timeline-box bg-primary text-primary-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 1</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>1,940개 대만 수출기업의 두 공식 데이터셋을 이용해 U자/역U자 회귀모형을 추정했다.</p></div><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-primary'></div></div><hr class='bg-primary'/></li><li><hr class='bg-secondary'/><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-secondary'></div></div><div class='timeline-end timeline-box bg-secondary text-secondary-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 2</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>핵심 변수·사례·대상을 정리한다.</p></div><hr class='bg-secondary'/></li><li><hr class='bg-accent'/><div class='timeline-middle'><div class='w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-accent'></div></div><div class='timeline-start timeline-box bg-accent text-accent-content'><p class='font-bold'>STEP 3</p><p class='text-xs mt-1'>저자들이 사용한 분석틀/모형을 적용한다.</p></div><hr class='bg-accent'/></li></ul><p class='mt-4 text-sm'><b>재현 가능성 평가:</b> 부분 재현 가능</p></div></div><div class='card bg-base-100 shadow'><div class='card-body'><h2 class='card-title border-l-4 border-accent pl-3 text-xl mb-4'>STEP 5 — Limitation 분리</h2><div class='alert alert-error mb-4'><span class='font-bold'>A. 논문이 스스로 인정한 한계</span><span class='ml-2'>단일 기업·국가 표본에 묶인 일반화 한계</span></div><div class='collapse collapse-arrow bg-warning/10'><input type='checkbox'/><div class='collapse-title font-medium'>B. 논문이 언급하지 않았지만 비판적으로 의심할 점</div><div class='collapse-content'><p>횡단면/관측자료라 역인과와 미관측 교란을 완전히 제거하긴 어렵다.</p></div></div></div></div></div>",
